---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Medical Practice Accounting — CA Accounting"
  description="Accounting, bookkeeping, and tax services for doctors, dentists, chiropractors, veterinarians and other medical practitioners in California."
>
  <section class="bg-cream-warm py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 fade-in">Industries · Medical Practices</p>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-navy leading-tight mb-6 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          Practice management, bookkeeping, and tax strategy.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-charcoal text-lg leading-relaxed fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
          Doctors, dentists, chiropractors, veterinarians and other medical practitioners will benefit from our combination of practice management solutions, bookkeeping services and tax strategies.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-16">
        <div class="lg:col-span-1 fade-in">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-4">What we handle</h2>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
            Medical practices share a common set of financial considerations. Our work for medical clients combines bookkeeping, tax strategy, and ongoing practice management support.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Accounting and bookkeeping</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Outsourced accounting and bookkeeping for medical practices.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Tax preparation and planning</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Annual tax return preparation and year-round tax minimization planning.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Payroll services</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Fully outsourced payroll processing.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Practice management consulting</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Consulting designed for the operational realities of running a practice.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Practice valuation</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Valuation of medical practices.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Practice mergers and acquisitions</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">M&A support on the buy or sell side of a practice transition.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Controls analysis</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Analysis of internal controls within the practice.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Annual cost reporting</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Annual cost reporting for medical practices that require it.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">QuickBooks setup and training</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">QuickBooks setup and staff training tailored to the practice.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Business incorporation</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Entity formation and incorporation services for new practices.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-navy text-cream py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="fade-in">
          <p class="text-cream/60 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Who we work with</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-cream mb-6">
            Practitioners and the practices they run.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-cream/80 text-base leading-relaxed">
            Solo practitioners, partnerships, and multi-location groups across California. Whether you operate a single practice or several, the financial work scales with your business.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-cream/70 text-sm fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Doctors and physicians</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Dentists and oral hygienists</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Chiropractors</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Veterinarians</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Hospice providers</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Assisted living facilities</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Home healthcare providers</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Healthcare management companies</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-cream-warm py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-6">
          Ready to talk?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-10">
          Schedule a free initial consultation. We will review where the practice is today and tell you how we can help.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="btn-modern inline-block bg-forest text-cream font-semibold px-10 py-4 rounded hover:bg-forest-hover transition-colors"
        >
          Schedule a Free Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
